cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object pose estimation from RGB-D images using deep learning techniques. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the application of the proposed approach in robotic systems. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning models for classification and regression tasks. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with intelligent systems that can estimate the pose of objects in cluttered scenes. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on generating or rendering graphics, but rather on estimating the pose of real-world objects.
